-- Daimler Says Electric Vehicle Partnership With BYD to Be Limited to China
-- B y   M a k i k o   K i t a m u r a
-- 2010-10-12T02:17:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-12/daimler-says-byd-electric-vehicle-partnership-limited-to-china.html
Daimler AG’s electric vehicle
partnership with BYD Co. will be limited to China, Pitt Moos,
project manager for the German company’s Smart brand said in
Tokyo today.  Daimler will use its own batteries in electric vehicles and
hybrids outside of China, Moos said. BYD and Daimler will sell
electric cars under a new brand in China, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Makiko Kitamura in Tokyo at 
